<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Dec1937"><font color="red">20 December 1937</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): hold back for a couple of weeks at least the pages of corrections and additions to Part II which Mr Joyce has entrusted to you for me &hellip; I am sorry to hear that Mr Joyce is still working at such tremendous pressure and through the greater part of the night. </div>
